{"tid":1710511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母呀郭位","createTime":"2019-11-12T07:52:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T08:04:36.000Z","uid":53533,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"25fbb425d8a432778421151ec1bb099413034921","tid":1710511,"uid":53533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"各位同事，同學及校友：<br />\n<br />\n鄭翼之樓及校長辦公室於昨天晚上遭到惡意刑事破壞，多處地方受損毁，其間更有城大學生組織記者把非法暴力破壞行為即時上網。大學強烈譴責所有刑事破壞行為，並對相關人等保留一切法律及其他責任的追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n大學將成立調查委會，調查事件及確定渉案人士，如查出有城大學生涉案，將會以既定紀律處分程序，嚴肅處理。<br />\n<br />\n校長郭位教授<br />\n學務副校長任廣禹教授<br />\n副校長（研究及科技）及研究生院院長呂堅教授<br />\n副校長（學生事務）葉豪盛教授<br />\n副校長（發展及對外關係）李國安教授<br />\n副校長（行政）李惠光先生<br />\n秘書長林群聲教授<br />\n學務長崔永康教授<br />\n署理傳訊及公關處處長袁國傑教授<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦郭位"},{"pid":"3290e62a8b726ece6fd15a97fb817ed2b783c2e0","tid":1710511,"uid":53440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:54:30.000Z","msg":"郭位比狗屌"},{"pid":"fbb24b3229a071fe4a19b597819cd791922df0b6","tid":1710511,"uid":61032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"呢條廢老幾時先肯死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49acc04619a0a9cde6543da77ff10a6219ec7d04","tid":1710511,"uid":36134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"畜生"},{"pid":"773b7d68fd43a6fb531b97243bf8b730b28edbbd","tid":1710511,"uid":39215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"郭位第一時間篤咗灰"},{"pid":"82272e64347184f6e666e152dff9a4aba4ba4176","tid":1710511,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:59:20.000Z","msg":"奶共台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d960e5037708cbc85a35053d1363e262349083a7","tid":1710511,"uid":28960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy